No. 225,

Misc.

Anselmi v. Attorney General of the United States et al. Petitioner pro se. Acting Solicitor General Stern, Assistant Attorney General Olney, Beatrice Rosenberg and Felicia Dubrovsky for the United States et al., respondents.
